        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2724",
        "content": "Then said the judge, \"Of what family or race are you?\"--\"What does it concern you,\" answered Alban, \"of what stock I am?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
